summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 34E & 34W page 98 & 99 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Supplemental Plat of G. Kinnear's Addition, Lots 6-14, incl., Block 28, Lots 6-10, incl., Block 27, Lots 7-10, incl., Block 22, Lots 4-15, incl., Block B, Supplemental Plat of Block 20 of Supplemental Plat of G. Kinnear's Addition, Lots 1-18, incl., Block 19, Supplemental Plat of G. Kinnear's Addition, from Multiple Residence High Density (RMH) Zone to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM) Zone, located along Olympic Place from 3rd Ave. W. to 8th Ave. W.
